[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1683","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1683.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1011","title":"Microsoft Data Access Components (MDAC) RDS 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Microsoft Data Access Components (MDAC) 中的远程数据服务 (RDS) DataFactory 组件暴露了不安全的内部方法，远程攻击者可通过 IIS 发送特制的 HTTP 请求，利用该组件绕过安全限制直接执行任意系统命令。该漏洞影响 IIS 3.0/4.0、MDAC 2.1 等组件，攻击无需身份认证，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。微软已发布安全公告及补丁修复此漏洞。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1011"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:31.110","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-025 提供的补丁，或升级至 Windows 2000 及以上版本（默认禁用 RDS DataFactory）。如无法升级，删除注册表键 `HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Services\\W3SVC\\Parameters\\ADCLaunch\\RDSServer.DataFactory` 以禁用该危险组件，同时在 IIS 管理器中移除 `/msadc/` 虚拟目录映射。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-054.shtml","http://www.osvdb.org/272","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-004","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-025","https://www.securityfocus.com/bid/529","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19424","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1011.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1011","https://github.com/fankh/vulnerability-poc/blob/e4734a5d374932e0e8adfb714d6049181237b752/1999/CVE-1999-1011/README.md","https://github.com/e-m-b-a/emba/blob/968abdc74763b43a3cdd216fbb1950cab484f982/config/msf_cve-db.txt","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1011.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1011.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1011.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qcm7-2qvw-4c58/GHSA-qcm7-2qvw-4c58.json","https://github.com/decal/werdlists/blob/81edb463f7f6311c85defefaf75ac9cd58e5cfb9/exploit-info/symantec-attack-signatures.txt","https://github.com/Chudry/Xerror/blob/07ec57cabcd27cdb47c89af452bdf4ed07207347/xerror/parsing/msf_module_result/msf_module_cve.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1683.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1683.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1683.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1700","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1700.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1086","title":"Novell NetWare IPX 管理会话伪骗权限提升漏洞","description":"Novell NetWare 5及更早版本在IPX协议上运行且数据包签名级别低于3时存在安全漏洞。远程攻击者可通过伪造IPC分片数据包中的MAC地址来欺骗NetWare核心协议(NCP)调用，从而在未经授权的情况下获取管理员权限。该漏洞危害严重，CVSS评分10.0，可导致目标系统完全受控。建议升级数据包签名级别至3或以上以进行防护。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1086"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-15T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:41.520","remediation":"将 NetWare 服务器 NCF 文件中 `SET PACKET SIGNATURE LEVEL` 设置为 3 或更高，强制要求 IPX 数据包签名验证，防止 MAC 地址欺骗攻击。如无法调整签名级别，可考虑禁用 IPX 协议并迁移至 TCP/IP 网络，或使用 VLAN 隔离限制攻击来源。建议升级至 Novell 6 及以上版本以获得完整修复。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93214475111651&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/528","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1086.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1086","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1086.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1086.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1086.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qhf9-4cg8-h46m/GHSA-qhf9-4cg8-h46m.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1086.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000696.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1700.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0995","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0995.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1166","title":"Linux Kernel 2.0.37 Segment Limit 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Linux Kernel 2.0.37 版本中对于自定义段限制（Segment Limit）的编码处理存在缺陷，导致本地攻击者能够通过访问并修改内核内存来提升权限至 root。该漏洞源于内核未正确验证段限长值，使得低权限用户可利用特定系统调用绕过内存访问限制。攻击者需拥有本地系统账户并具备代码执行能力，成功利用后可完全控制目标系统。该漏洞影响 Linux Kernel 2.0.37 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1166"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:51.663","remediation":"建议立即升级 Linux 内核至 2.0.38 或更高版本（如 2.2.x 系列），该漏洞在内核 2.0.38 中已修复。若无法升级，可通过限制本地用户对 /dev/mem 和 /dev/kmem 的访问权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/18156","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/523","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19419"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0995.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0574","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0574.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0809","title":"Netscape Communicator Cookie 安全策略绕过漏洞","description":"Netscape Communicator 4.x 版本存在安全绕过漏洞。当用户启用 JavaScript 且已选择\"仅接受来自正浏览页面同一服务器之 Cookie\"选项时，浏览器仍不会对 Cookie 设置行为发出警告。攻击者可利用恶意网页绕过 Cookie 同源策略，跨站设置或窃取用户 Cookie，导致用户隐私泄露或会话劫持。漏洞影响 Netscape Communicator 4.x 全系版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0809"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:06.117","remediation":"停止使用 Netscape Communicator 4.x，升级至 Mozilla Firefox 或其它现代浏览器，并在浏览器设置中禁用 JavaScript 作为临时缓解措施。对于仍必须使用 Netscape 的场景，可在浏览器首选项中关闭 JavaScript 功能（Edit → Preferences → Advanced → Scripts & Plugins → 取消启用 JavaScript）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0809"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0574.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0453","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0453.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0752","title":"Netscape Enterprise Server SSL Handshake 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Netscape Enterprise Server 的 SSL 握手处理过程中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标服务器发送特制的 SSL 握手请求触发该溢出，导致服务进程崩溃从而引发拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Netscape Enterprise Server 3.6 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0752"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:58.993","remediation":"建议将 Netscape Enterprise Server 升级至 4.0 或更高版本以修复 SSL 握手缓冲区溢出漏洞。由于该产品已停止维护，长期方案应迁移至仍在支持的 Web 服务器（如 Apache HTTP Server 或 Nginx）。临时缓解措施可在网络层限制异常 SSL 握手请求频率。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0752","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19416"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0453.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0509","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0509.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0728","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 键盘鼠标 IOCTL 权限许可与访问控制漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统存在权限控制缺陷，本地用户可直接调用控制键盘和鼠标的 IOCTL 设备控制指令，无需管理员权限即可禁用输入设备。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 等版本，攻击者需具备本地登录权限，成功利用后可导致系统输入功能失效，属于本地权限滥用型漏洞。CVSS 评分 7.8，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0728"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:55.960","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-024 提供的补丁程序，该补丁已在 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 5 及后续版本中集成。对于仍在运行 Windows NT 4.0 的系统，应立即升级到受支持的操作系统版本（如 Windows Server 2016/2019/2022）。临时缓解措施：限制非授权用户对服务器的交互式登录权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ236359","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-024"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0509.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1306","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1306.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0918","title":"Microsoft Windows IGMP 报文处理拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows 95/98/NT 3.51/NT 4.0/2000 的 IGMP 协议实现存在输入验证缺陷（CWE-20），远程攻击者可向目标系统发送特制的分片 IGMP 数据包，触发协议栈解析异常，导致目标系统蓝屏崩溃或服务完全停止。该漏洞无需用户交互即可远程触发，影响所有受支持的 Windows 9x/NT 系列版本，攻击者只需发送少量畸形数据包即可造成拒绝服务。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0918"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:19.657","remediation":"Windows 95/98 用户请通过 Microsoft Windows Update 安装安全更新或下载 MS99-034 补丁（KB Q238329）；Windows NT 4.0 用户请安装 Service Pack 6a 及后续安全汇总。上述系统均已终止支持，建议升级至 Windows 10/11 或 Windows Server 2016 以上版本。临时缓解措施：在边界防火墙上禁用 IGMP 协议或过滤碎片化 IGMP 报文。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ238329","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/514","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-034","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19415"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1306.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0248","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0248.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0688","title":"HP 软件分发器 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"HP-UX 系统的软件分发器（Software Distributor，简称 SD）在 10.x 与 11.x 版本中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。该漏洞源于 SD 组件在处理特定输入时未对数据长度做充分边界校验，导致攻击者可控的过长数据写入固定大小的缓冲区，进而可覆盖相邻内存并可能实现任意代码执行。影响范围为运行 HPUX 10.x 和 11.x 且启用 SD 服务的系统。攻击条件为攻击者需能够向目标系统的 SD 服务发送特制请求，通常需要一定的本地或相邻网络访问权限。利用方式为构造恶意输入触发缓冲区溢出，造成服务异常或提升权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0688"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:51.047","remediation":"立即安装 HP-UX 11.11 或更高版本的 HP Software Distributor 补丁 HPD4365-11，或者应用 HPSBUX9907-101 安全更新。如需继续使用 HPUX 10.x，请应用 HP SD 10.20 补丁套件。立即更新系统，关闭不必要的 SD 服务以降低风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/545","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9907-101","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0688.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0688","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0688.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0688.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-873q-3c4x-555r/GHSA-873q-3c4x-555r.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0688.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/VulnerabilityHistoryProject/mega-foss/blob/4829eeb7b0101570abbc87d2a697f2c0c2f4e5c3/src/cve/graphql/trial.json","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--9b15c9ce-60ad-4d9f-bb76-76ab2ab118a8.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0248.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0254","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0254.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0690","title":"HP CDE 将当前目录加入 root 的 PATH 环境变量导致权限提升漏洞","description":"HP CDE（Common Desktop Environment）在设置 root 用户环境变量 PATH 时错误地将当前目录 \".\" 包含在内，导致本地攻击者可在任意目录中放置与系统命令同名的恶意程序，当 root 用户通过 su 或登录进入该目录并执行未指定路径的命令时，恶意程序将以 root 权限自动执行，实现本地提权。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 系统中运行 CDE 的版本，需要攻击者拥有本地 shell 访问权限，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0690"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:51.300","remediation":"编辑 root 用户的 .profile、.login 或 CDE 系统级配置文件 /etc/dt/config/Xsession.d/ 下的相关脚本，移除 PATH 中的当前目录（即删除 \".\" 或空路径项），确保 PATH 仅包含绝对路径的系统目录（如 /usr/bin:/usr/sbin）。同时建议修改 CDE 启动脚本中 PATH 的拼接方式，使用完整路径调用命令，消除当前目录隐式搜索带来的提权风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-053.shtml","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9907-100","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0690.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0690","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0690.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0690.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rf75-mr45-vgcx/GHSA-rf75-mr45-vgcx.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_300_400.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0690.json","https://github.com/Team-Atlanta/aixcc-asc-atlantis/blob/785c446f980e12155935db586aa30c3b54adcc86/crs/src/crs-patch/smith/smith/lib/cwe/raw/CWE-427.txt","https://github.com/CyberSecAI/CWE-Expert/blob/f634e911e6c24a1ad8b9619383e2ab3eb2d9ebd4/CWE_corpus/markdown/4_cwe_trimmed_top25.md.txt","https://github.com/ws-researcher/CAEA/blob/098ddb07c83845feda3d1b1d56ef634927954af4/KGA/dataSet/ICNS/entN_ids_1"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0254.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0296","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0296.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0707","title":"HP Visualize Conference FTP 默认配置未授权文件发送漏洞","description":"HP Visualize Conference 的默认 FTP 配置存在授权缺陷，会议参与者可在未经授权的情况下向其他与会者发送文件。攻击者利用该配置漏洞可通过 FTP 传输恶意文件至目标用户系统，结合社会工程学手段诱导用户执行，可能导致任意代码执行或系统被控制。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 系统上的 Visualize Conference 组件，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高，需通过限制 FTP 服务权限或安装厂商补丁进行修复。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0707"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:53.430","remediation":"立即安装 HP 安全公告 HPSBUX9906-099 中提供的 Visualize Conference 安全补丁。同时修改 FTP 配置文件，限制未授权用户的文件传输权限，仅允许已认证的会议参与者进行文件收发。如不需要 FTP 功能，建议直接禁用 Visualize Conference 内置的 FTP 服务，并在防火墙上限制相关端口的访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-050.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/493","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9906-099"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0296.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0308","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0308.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0696","title":"多厂商 CDE Calendar Manager Service Daemon (rpc.cmsd) 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"CDE 日历管理服务守护进程（rpc.cmsd）存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的 RPC 请求触发该漏洞，导致拒绝服务或任意代码执行。该漏洞影响 Caldera OpenUnix 8.0/UnixWare 7.1.1、HP HP-UX 11.0、Solaris 7.0 及 SunOS 4.1.4 等多个 Unix 操作系统版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用此漏洞。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0696"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:52.067","remediation":"建议立即安装各厂商对应安全补丁：Solaris 7.0 安装补丁 106827-01 或 106828-01，HP-UX 11.0 安装 PHSS_19757 补丁，UnixWare 7.1.1 安装 erg711905 补丁。如无法打补丁，可在 inetd.conf 中注释掉 rpc.cmsd 服务行并重启 inetd，或在防火墙层面阻止对 611/TCP 端口的访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/188","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-051.shtml","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9908-102","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19421","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0696.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0696","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0696.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0696.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/1907.txt","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-h3qp-3qwx-3x56/GHSA-h3qp-3qwx-3x56.json","https://github.com/NetBSD/pkgsrc-wip/blob/6723edd43ced2a9627d0c0e8bf12d208cfde84d5/sara/PLIST","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/bailehang/snort_2.2.0/blob/34f8a3a85f15645aea53d6e0d46863c7c57e43ef/doc/signatures/1909.txt","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/2011/gb_cde_rpc_cmsd_service_detect.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0308.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0681","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0681.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0889","title":"Cisco 675路由器远程登录会话漏洞","description":"Cisco 675 路由器运行 CBOS 操作系统时存在未授权访问漏洞。如果管理员未设置 exec 或 superuser 密码，远程攻击者可通过 Telnet 协议直接建立登录会话，获得路由器的完全管理控制权限。攻击者无需任何认证即可访问设备，进而可能修改网络配置、窃取传输数据或发起进一步攻击。该漏洞影响 Cisco 675 系列路由器，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。建议管理员立即设置强密码或升级固件以修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0889"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:16.070","remediation":"立即为 Cisco 675 路由器设置 exec 和 superuser 密码（通过 `set password` 和 `set superuser-password` 命令），并配置访问控制列表限制 telnet 源 IP。建议升级到 CBOS 最新版本或更换支持 SSH 的现代设备，同时禁用非必要的 telnet 服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/39"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0681.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0004","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0004.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0140","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 RAS/PPTP 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 3.51 及 NT 4.0 的远程访问服务（RAS）与 PPTP 协议实现中存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，通过向目标系统发送特制的畸形控制数据包，可导致 RAS/PPTP 服务崩溃或停止响应，造成系统无法正常提供远程访问功能。该漏洞无需用户交互即可远程触发，影响范围涉及企业远程接入环境，可能导致业务中断。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0140"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-06-30T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:40.957","remediation":"安装 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 4 或更高版本以修复 RAS/PPTP 协议处理中的缺陷。由于 Windows NT 4.0 已停止支持，建议升级至受支持的 Windows Server 版本（如 Windows Server 2019/2022），并在防火墙上限制对 PPTP 端口（TCP 1723）的访问以降低暴露风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0140","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20508","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0140.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0140","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0140.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0140.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0140.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fg49-hp4g-2h7r/GHSA-fg49-hp4g-2h7r.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/W/winnt_pptp_dos.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0140.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0004.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0508","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0508.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0726","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 映像头拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 可执行文件加载器在处理 PE 格式映像头时存在输入验证不足漏洞（CWE-20）。本地攻击者可通过构造包含畸形映像头字段（如数据目录项或节表偏移）的恶意 .exe 文件，诱使用户执行后触发未处理异常，导致系统蓝屏崩溃（BSOD），造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 Workstation/Server 及 Terminal Server Edition，需用户交互触发。微软已在 Service Pack 5 中修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0726"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-30T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:55.700","remediation":"Windows NT 4.0 已停止支持且无安全更新可用，建议升级至 Windows Server 2008 及以上版本。如无法升级，可在组策略中限制用户执行非信任程序，并使用进程审计日志监控异常 PE 加载行为作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ234557","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/499","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-023"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0508.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0715","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0715.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0916","title":"WebTrends 账户口令文件权限许可漏洞","description":"WebTrends 软件在安装目录中以明文文件存储账户名和密码，且该文件未设置充分的访问权限限制，导致本地攻击者可通过读取该文件获取敏感凭据信息。攻击者获得凭据后可进一步利用其他服务或系统资源，造成信息泄露。该漏洞影响 WebTrends 多个版本，利用条件为攻击者需具备本地文件系统访问权限。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0916"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-29T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:19.420","remediation":"将存储用户名和密码的文件（如 web.ini、wtlogin.txt）的 NTFS 权限设置为仅 SYSTEM 和管理员可读取，移除 Everyone 和 Users 组的访问权限；升级 WebTrends 到最新受支持版本；启用 Windows 集成身份验证或加密存储方式替代明文密码文件；定期审计关键文件的 ACL 配置。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0916"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0715.toml"}]